<http://iflastandards.info/ns/lrm/lrmoo/F30_Manifestation_Creation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class comprises the activities of selecting, arranging and presenting one or more instances of F2 Expression on a carrier or other persistent presentation means with the purpose of communicating it to some public. It includes the specification of the presentation as to sensory impression (such as visual appearance or audio rendition)."@en .
