<http://iflastandards.info/ns/lrm/lrmoo/R76_is_derivative_of> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This property associates an instance of F2 Expression with another instance of F2 Expression which was its source or one of its sources. This property is not transitive. It is asymmetric and irreflexive. This property is also a shortcut of the fully developed path: F2 Expression (1). P16i was used for : F28 Expression Creation. R17 created : F2 Expression (2)."@en .
