<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P72_has_language> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This property associates an instance(s) of E33 Linguistic Object with an instance of E56 Language in which it is, at least partially, expressed.\nLinguistic Objects are composed in one or more human languages. This property allows these languages to be documented."@en .
