<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P67_refers_to> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This property documents that an instance of E89 Propositional Object makes a statement about an instance of E1 CRM Entity. P67 refers to (is referred to by) has the P67.1 has type link to an instance of E55 Type. This is intended to allow a more detailed description of the type of reference. This differs from P129 is about (is subject of), which describes the primary subject or subjects of the instance of E89 Propositional Object."@en .
