<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P44i_is_condition_of> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "est l'état matériel de"@fr .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P98i_was_born> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "γεννήθηκε"@el .
