<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P55_has_current_location> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This property records the location of an instance of E19 Physical Object at the time of validity of the record or database containing the statement that uses this property.\nThis property is a specialisation of P53 has former or current location (is former or current location of). It indicates that the instance of E53 Place associated with the instance of E19 Physical Object is the current location of the object. The property does not allow any indication of how long the object has been at the current location.\nThis property is a shortcut. A more detailed representation can make use of the fully developed (i.e., indirect) path from E19 Physical Object, through, P25i moved by, E9 Move, P26 moved to to E53 Place if and only if this Move is the most recent."@en .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E39_Actor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Akteur"@de .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P91i_is_unit_of> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E54_Dimension> .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E39_Actor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Agente"@pt .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P16_used_specific_object> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P16i_was_used_for> .
<https://www.cao-crm.eu/ontology/> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "CAO_CRM 1.0 (julio de 2026) -- primera versión hecha pública, compuesta de CIDOC-CRM 7.1.3, LRMoo 1.1.1 y CRMdig 5.0"@es .
